救，會哭著喊著說醫生你救救我&hellip;&hellip;伴隨著劇烈地掙扎，直到呼出最後一口氣。<br />\n<br />\n根據該帖文，新冠肺炎重症病人死亡前的<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>3個步痛苦過程分別是漸進式窒息、痛苦爭扎、慘叫身亡。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n該醫生甚至直指，「死因本質上和淹死一個道理」，「大量的水，進到了肺裡面之後，氧進不去，肺被病毒導致的果凍狀的分泌物給佔滿了，換氣功能完全喪失，再濃的氧也進不去血裡面；而吸痰也沒用，因為靠氣管鏡到達不了那個終末端的地方」。<br />\n<br />\n隨後，文章強調，新冠肺炎沒有特效藥<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2569492/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E7%97%9B%E8%8B%A6%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E9%81%8E%E7%A8%8B%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E3%80%80%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%AC%E8%B3%AA%E5%A6%82%E5%90%8C%E6%B5%B8%E6%AD%BB?mtc=10012\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2569492%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E%25E6%2582%25A3%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2597%259B%25E8%258B%25A6%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25A1%25E9%2581%258E%25E7%25A8%258B%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589%25E3%2580%2580%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%25B7%259A%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%259C%25AC%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E5%25A6%2582%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%25B5%25B8%25E6%25AD%25BB%3Fmtc%3D10012&d=vOjfDEnLED7uJ%2BqF6s3OfdDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=b4aecd96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2569492/%E3%80%90%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E7%97%9B%E8%8B%A6%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%A1%E9%81%8E%E7%A8%8B%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E3%80%80%E5%89%8D%E7%B7%9A%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%AC%E8%B3%AA%E5%A6%82%E5%90%8C%E6%B5%B8%E6%AD%BB?mtc=10012</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:26:39.000Z","msg":"有幾多%人會咁?"},{"pid":"111d364067f889a48da5f6a29b65c12369c7b8bc","tid":1888360,"uid":199670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:27:06.000Z","msg":"肺炎都係咁架啦？"},{"pid":"fd6aa8fb01ae